OL,3,CWoman in hospital after suspected hit
OL,4,Cand run with Deliveroo rider
OL,6,FA woman is in a life threatening
OL,7,Fcondition in hospital following a
OL,8,Fsuspected hit and run involving a
OL,9,FDeliveroo rider in Reading.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,FCaversham Road, near Great Knollys
OL,13,FStreet at 8.50pm on Wednesday 18
OL,14,FFebruary, to reports of a collision
OL,15,Finvolving an e-bike and a pedestrian
OL,16,Fwho was walking with a red trolley bag.
OL,18,FPolice say the victim, a woman in her
OL,19,Fsixties sustained life-threatening
OL,20,Finjuries, requiring hospital
OL,21,Ftreatment, where she remains.
