OL,3,CWoman in hospital after suspected hit
OL,4,Cand run with Deliveroo rider
OL,6,FInvestigating officer PC Jamie Payne
OL,7,Fof the Roads Policing Unit said: "I am
OL,8,Fappealing to anyone who witnessed this
OL,9,Fcollision to please get in contact.
OL,11,F"I am also appealing to anyone who was
OL,12,Fdriving in the area at this time to
OL,13,Fplease check for dash-cam footage that
OL,14,Fcould have captured the collision or
OL,15,Fthe moments leading up to or after it.
OL,17,F"If you have any information that
OL,18,Fcould assist our investigation, please
OL,19,Fcall 101 or make an online report, via
OL,20,Four website, quoting reference number
OL,21,F43260083451"
